Task 2 – Simulation Demonstration

To better illustrate how the perception system works, we also recorded
a short video showing the simulation of the perception pipeline.

The video demonstrates the following:

- The simulated chess board environment in Gazebo
- Detection of ArUco markers from the camera view
- Mapping of detected markers to board coordinates
- Reconstruction of the 6 × 6 board configuration

This video provides a clearer understanding of how the perception
module processes visual input and converts it into a board state
that can be used by the game engine.

